<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_501a8531-be96-4ab2-af96-c8731407cbde" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="WA"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>I4D5</sptc><title id="_29c6ce77-33f9-4392-8d17-71a5da096650">Handrails to ramps, flights and landings</title><archive-num>2019: WA H101.4</archive-num><subclause id="_9e68d244-513c-43c8-bf2c-857b8b834ced" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_04e64491-b854-4627-960c-de98148c0759">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>For a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2508_4.3.0.xml#_da789fac-c334-4952-a23b-ac344815d25a" id="_502a2bbc-0e69-46af-b468-359c996a0169" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">WA public building</xref>, handrails must be located along—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_21fe62e9-fbfd-4947-8a35-cd227d00c19e">both sides of a ramp or flight; and</li><li id="_e98c18a3-9ddc-43ab-a4cb-51d325fc5316">each side of a landing, except for that part of a side that is interrupted by a ramp or flight.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_9c68bad5-d01c-4aaa-b090-2766ac36ec10" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_c3c3b8f7-f6ae-4c46-970e-73debfd076b2">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>The requirements of (1) do not apply to—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_5743fbbc-032c-4b7e-a825-af701da9711e">handrails referred to in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1684_1.2.0.xml#_143d5dc3-c1c4-4895-a4c3-ead151730348" id="_9f25ce6b-5130-4ae3-9228-7b92a5dabec5" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">D3D23</xref>; or</li><li id="_915df098-24ef-416b-8df6-13ede69e2f37">handrails located within a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1285_2.1.0.xml#_c71e675e-d6e1-4612-8e59-381a56e224a8" id="_8fc4eb49-09a1-43ff-91d7-eddbf3b6a428" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">fire-isolated stairway</xref> or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1284_2.0.0.xml#_cfa6cc89-aa6c-4eaf-90e6-8aabe04b9c76" id="_2fc0f2f2-8eae-468e-a919-57328ab77724" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">fire-isolated ramp</xref>.</li></ol></subclause></clause>